---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Laser Cutting & Punching | ICM Factory Direct">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <PageHero
    title="Laser Punching"
    breadcrumbs={[
      { label: "Home", href: "/" },
      { label: "Product Features", href: "#" },
      { label: "Laser Punching" }
    ]}
    backgroundImage="/images/worker-in-textile-industry-sewing-FQEGPTY-1.jpg"
    overlayOpacity={0.6}
    overlayColor="#1D2F40"
  />

  <!-- Content Section - From XML -->
  <section class="py-[80px] bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-[15px]">
      <!-- Title -->
      <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-semibold leading-[1.3] text-[#1D2F40] mb-4">Precision Fabrication for the World of Fabrics</h4>
      
      <!-- Image floated right -->
      <div class="float-right ml-8 mb-4 w-[45%]">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] shadow-lg">
          <img src="/images/laser.jpg" alt="Laser Punching" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content that wraps around image -->
      <div class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.7] text-[#4A4A4A] space-y-4">
        <p>Unlike traditional fabric cutting methods, our advanced Laser Punching system brings a new level of accuracy, design flexibility, and efficiency to fabric processing. This cutting-edge technology ensures that every piece is crafted with meticulous precision, meeting the highest standards of quality and customization.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Here's how our Laser Punching process works for fabrics:</strong></p>
        
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li><strong>Design Creation:</strong> Our expert designers use specialized software to translate your ideas into intricate digital patterns, ready for fabrication.</li>
          <li><strong>Material Preparation:</strong> We carefully prepare the fabric, ensuring proper tension, alignment, and smoothness for precise Laser Punching.</li>
          <li><strong>Laser Cutting:</strong> Our powerful laser beam precisely cuts the fabric, following the intricate digital patterns, resulting in clean edges and precise shapes.</li>
          <li><strong>Punching:</strong> Simultaneously, our advanced punching machine uses punches and dies to create holes, perforations, or decorative features on the fabric, enhancing its functionality and aesthetic appeal.</li>
          <li><strong>Finishing Touches:</strong> Once Laser Punching is complete, our skilled craftsmen add any necessary final touches, ensuring each fabric piece meets your exact specifications.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p><strong>By employing Laser Punching technology in fabric fabrication, we offer a range of remarkable advantages:</strong></p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li><strong>Unparalleled Precision:</strong> Laser Punching delivers clean, accurate cuts, and precise perforations, even on delicate or intricate fabric designs.</li>
          <li><strong>Design Freedom:</strong> Our Laser Punching capabilities unlock a world of design possibilities, allowing for complex patterns, decorative elements, and customization that elevates your fabric products.</li>
          <li><strong>Increased Efficiency:</strong> Laser Punching automates the fabric fabrication process, reducing production time and increasing overall efficiency, ensuring prompt delivery of your orders.</li>
          <li><strong>Enhanced Functionality:</strong> With precise punching, we can incorporate functional features like ventilation, moisture control, or attachment points in the fabric, enhancing its performance and utility.</li>
          <li><strong>Diverse Applications:</strong> Laser Punching technology is suitable for various fabric applications, including apparel, home textiles, upholstery, automotive interiors, and more.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Join us on the cutting edge of fabric fabrication by experiencing the power of Laser Punching. Our expertise, combined with this state-of-the-art technology, ensures that your fabric products meet the highest standards of precision and innovation.</p>
        
        <p>Contact us today to discuss your fabric requirements and discover how Laser Punching can revolutionize your fabric-based project</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Clear float and button -->
      <div class="clear-both mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-[#1D2F40] text-[#1D2F40] hover:bg-[#1D2F40] hover:text-white font-nav text-[14px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] uppercase py-[12px] px-[30px] transition-colors">
          CONTACT US
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
